Title: iNevel
Plot: Carly, Sam and Freddie want their show to be reviewed. Carly risks receiving a bad review when she insults the annoying eleven year old who runs a popular site that rates web casts.
GuestStars: Reed Alexander (Nevel Papperman),  Colin Spensor (Wesley),  Nathan Pearson (Jeremy),  Wendy Braun (Mrs. Patterson)
